{"view":"article","slug":"fmc-hta","category":"FMC","subcategory":null,"topDir":"FMC","title":{"en":"人类西斯尔思韦特法 (HTA)"},"content":{"en":"<p><strong>人类西斯尔思韦特法 (HTA)</strong></p><p>HTA (Human Thistlethwaite Algorithm) 由Ryan Heise发明, 它将计算机使用的西斯尔思韦特法 (TA, Thistlethwaite Algorithm, EO-&gt;DR-&gt;HTR-&gt;finish，现在称为DR/HTR法) 步骤拆解为子步骤, 以便人类求解. 本文假设白顶绿前. 本文一般不给出左右和前后镜像情况. 转体可做x2/y2/z2. </p><p><strong>EO</strong></p><p>见\"EO\"页.</p><p><strong>DR</strong></p><p><strong>双十字 (Crosses)</strong></p><p>从这里开始不能做F*/B*. 这里将所有的对色视为一种颜色, 例如白和黄. 让顶底面的棱是白或黄, 即E棱归层 (E-Edge Separation) . 图中的黄色代表黄或白. </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>F2L基态公式</strong></p><p>用和<a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>基态类似的公式让顶底面非白黄棱放到E层白黄棱</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>还可这样放置</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong> <img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R'\">R U' R'</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U2 R U R'\">U2 R U R'</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U R U2' R'\">U R U2' R'</span></p><p>R可替换为r</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U L\">L' U L</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U2 L' U L\">U2 L' U L</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U L' U2 L\">U L' U2 L</span></p><p>L可替换为l</p></td><td><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>CO</strong></p><p>若顶底面都是<a href=\"/alg/oll\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">OLL</a> (即7个十字OLL) , 则直接做OLL公式. </p><p>若顶底面都不是<a href=\"/alg/oll\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">OLL</a>, 若有面有≥2个转角, 则这面可找到3个角构成OLL的一部分, 做OLL公式后仅剩1个转角. 当顶底面分别有≤2个转角时, 将其中2个转角放到下图前2个情况的位置 (至少保证其中一个角的朝向和图中一样) 做公式.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' r2' D R\">R U' r2' D R</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U l2 D' L'\">L' U l2 D' L'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>HTR</strong></p><p><strong>角HTR</strong></p><p>这里采用的是完全还原所有角的策略。即角先法。公式中的U/D层转动均可换成双层。可使用类似SQ1的公式。</p><p><strong>OBL</strong></p><p>即UD角归层.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">  OO</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> II</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> XX</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>R2</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R2' U2' F2\">R2' U2' F2</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R2 U'D' R2'\">R2 U'D' R2'</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> VV</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> VV</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> IX</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">XI</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R2 U' R2'\">R2 U' R2'</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R2 U2'D' R2'\">R2 U2'D' R2'</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R2 D R2' D R2\">R2 D R2' D R2</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R2 U' R2' U' R2\">R2 U' R2' U' R2</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>PBL</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">NN</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">JJ</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">NJ</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">JN</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>可不做任何操作</strong></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↑R2' F2 R2\">↑R2' F2 R2</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↑(R2' U2' F2)2\">↑(R2' U2' F2)2</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↓R2 U' R2' U2' F2 U' R2\">↓R2 U' R2' U2' F2 U' R2</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↓y2 R2 U' B2 U2' R2' U' R2\">↓y2 R2 U' B2 U2' R2' U' R2</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R2 U' R2 U D R2 D' R2\">R2 U' R2 U D R2 D' R2</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↓(R2 U R2' U')2 R2\">↓(R2 U R2' U')2 R2</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↓(R2 D R2 D')2 R2\">↓(R2 D R2 D')2 R2</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">Jx</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">xJ</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">Nx</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">xN</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↑R' U L' U2 R U' R' U2 R L\">↑R' U L' U2 R U' R' U2 R L</span></p><p>J Perm</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↓R2 B2 U R2' U' R2 U R2' U' R2\">↓R2 B2 U R2' U' R2 U R2' U' R2</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↓F2 U2' (R2 U' R2' U2' F2 U' R2) U2' F2'\">↓F2 U2' (R2 U' R2' U2' F2 U' R2) U2' F2'</span></p><p>Y Perm</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↓F2 D2 (R2 D R2' D2 F2 D R2) D2 F2\">↓F2 D2 (R2 D R2' D2 F2 D R2) D2 F2</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>做AUDF让角还原或差180°.</p><p><strong>棱HTR</strong></p><p>预设只允许所有180°转动. 让M层红橙棱到LR层蓝绿棱. </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image52.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>F2 -&gt; 右图</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U R2' F2 R2 U'\">U R2' F2 R2 U'</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U M' U2 M U\">U M' U2 M U</span></p></td><td><p><strong>F2 -&gt; 右图</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U' L2 F2 L2' U\">U' L2 F2 L2' U</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U' M' U2 M U'\">U' M' U2 M U'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>此步骤结束后角可能被破坏, 用180°的AUDF和UD角归层 (II, XX) 和CP (NN) 公式还原角. </p><p><strong>HTR Finish (棱)</strong></p><p>判断棱循环类型, 比如3e, 2e2e, 2e4e, 2e2e3e等和它们的叠加. 用预设和这些公式, 还有桥式4c步骤还原. 预设可用QT.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>3e</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image54.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image56.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↑(R2' F2 R2 U2')2\">↑(R2' F2 R2 U2')2</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U2 M' U2 M\">U2 M' U2 M</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>2e2e</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image58.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image60.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image62.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image64.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(M2 U2)2\">(M2 U2)2</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↓(R2 U2')3\">↓(R2 U2')3</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image66.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image68.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image70.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image72.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image74.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image76.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(↑R2' U2' F2 R2) (F2' U2' R2' F2)\">(↑R2' U2' F2 R2) (F2' U2' R2' F2)</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(↑R2' F2 R2 U2') (F2' R2' F2 U2')\">(↑R2' F2 R2 U2') (F2' R2' F2 U2')</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(↑L2 F2' L2' U2) (F2 L2 F2 U2')\">(↑L2 F2' L2' U2) (F2 L2 F2 U2')</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"},"algs":["R U' R'","U2 R U R'","U R U2' R'","L' U L","U2 L' U L","U L' U2 L","R U' r2' D R","L' U l2 D' L'","R2' U2' F2","R2 U'D' R2'","R2 U' R2'","R2 U2'D' R2'","R2 D R2' D R2","R2 U' R2' U' R2","↑R2' F2 R2","↑(R2' U2' F2)2","↓R2 U' R2' U2' F2 U' R2","↓y2 R2 U' B2 U2' R2' U' R2","R2 U' R2 U D R2 D' R2","↓(R2 U R2' U')2 R2","↓(R2 D R2 D')2 R2","↑R' U L' U2 R U' R' U2 R L","↓R2 B2 U R2' U' R2 U R2' U' R2","↓F2 U2' (R2 U' R2' U2' F2 U' R2) U2' F2'","↓F2 D2 (R2 D R2' D2 F2 D R2) D2 F2","U R2' F2 R2 U'","U M' U2 M U","U' L2 F2 L2' U","U' M' U2 M U'","↑(R2' F2 R2 U2')2","U2 M' U2 M","(M2 U2)2","↓(R2 U2')3","(↑R2' U2' F2 R2) (F2' U2' R2' F2)","(↑R2' F2 R2 U2') (F2' R2' F2 U2')","(↑L2 F2' L2' U2) (F2 L2 F2 U2')"],"thumb":"/stats/data/alg/media/fmc-hta/en/image2.svg","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
